411
00:29:32,320 --> 00:29:34,315
Ďakujem za odvoz.

412
00:29:34,689 --> 00:29:38,445
Strachovali ste sa o všetky 
tie kruté komentáre.

413
00:29:38,794 --> 00:29:42,085
